01:11:07,200 --> 01:11:09,500
{\fs14\shad2\3a&H64&\2c&H8080FF&\3c&HFF0080&}是的  当然有目的了

1150
01:11:11,300 --> 01:11:12,700
{\fs14\shad2\3a&H64&\2c&H8080FF&\3c&HFF0080&}请讲

